{"tid":100311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[來生不做支那虎] 寧波動物園咬豚老虎被擊斃　支那賤畜傷重不治","createTime":"2017-01-30T01:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T03:34:45.000Z","uid":9348,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ce09eee157e9d9fcbbd40e023c2cdd3056f5de5","tid":100311,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T01:53:34.000Z","msg":"【寧波動物園咬人老虎被擊斃　男遊客傷重不治】<br />\n<br />\n中國寧波雅戈爾動物園發生老虎咬人事件，據《新京報》報道，傷者搶救無效不治。<br />\n<br />\n寧波雅戈爾動物園證實，事件發生於今日（1月29日）下午2時許，一名男子擅自跨過防護欄，結果被老虎拖咬至重傷，片段所見更是衣衫不整。當老虎把涉事者拖入生活區時，同時亦有多隻老虎走近，工作人員用炮仗、水槍及鳴槍驅趕。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生之後，動物園已經暫時關閉，而工作人員亦透露，咬人的老虎已被擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-29-2017/35572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-29-2017%2F35572&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=34cbe4fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-29-2017/35572</a><br />\n<br />\n#寧波動物園 #老虎<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母支那賤畜死都要害鳩隻老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔被擊斃都毒撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4582a7c8ab002d3bd06e1a19c6d162ae6d065513","tid":100311,"uid":5856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T01:55:07.000Z","msg":"找數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ee7e69c34216079432074ddc0c788656179247","tid":100311,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T01:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 